===Pronunciation===
:(US) SAMPA:/cVm.p{s/
:IPA:/'kɔmpæs/

===Definition===
=== Noun ===

'''compass'''

# A magnetic or electronic device used to determine the cardinal directions (usually [[magnetic_north]])
# A tool used to draw circles in geometry, carpentry, manufacture, etc...
:([[beam_compass]])
# (circular path?)
: M. Le Page Du Pratz, ''History of Louisiana'' (PG), p. 47
:: ''In going up the Missisippi'' (sic) '', we meet with nothing remarkable before we come to the Detour aux Anglois, the English Reach: in that part the river takes a large '''compass''';''

====Related terms====
*[[compass point]]
*[[compass swing]] the process used (usually on a boat or a plane) to check the accuracy of a compass

